      <p>The proportion of each type of SV to the total SV is calculated using <xref rid="FD2" ref-type="disp-formula">equations 2</xref>, <xref rid="FD3" ref-type="disp-formula">3</xref>, and <xref rid="FD4" ref-type="disp-formula">4</xref> as follows:
